<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css?v=2025012407">
    <meta name="description" content="<%= user && user.username ? user.username + '의 데드락' : '데드락' %> - 데드락 게임 정보 플랫폼">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <a href="/ko" class="logo">
                <% if (user && user.topHero) { %>
                    <img src="<%= user.topHero.image %>" alt="<%= user.topHero.name %>" width="40" height="40" style="border-radius: 8px; object-fit: cover;" title="주요 영웅: <%= user.topHero.name %> (<%= user.topHero.matches %>경기)">
                <% } else { %>
                    <img src="https://cdn.deadlock.coach/vpk/panorama/images/heroes/bebop_card.webp" alt="Bebop" width="40" height="40" style="border-radius: 8px; object-fit: cover;">
                <% } %>
                <span><%= user && user.username ? user.username + '의 데드락' : '데드락' %></span>
            </a>
            <div class="nav-right">
                <ul class="nav-links">
                    <li><a href="/ko/wiki">Wiki</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/ko/heroes">영웅</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/ko/items">아이템</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/ko/board">게시판</a></li>
                </ul>
                
                <select class="lang-selector">
                    <option value="ko">한국어</option>
                    <option value="en">English</option>
                </select>
                
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <div class="user-menu">
                        <img src="<%= user.avatar %>" alt="<%= user.username %>" class="user-avatar">
                        <span class="username"><%= user.username %></span>
                        <a href="/ko/profile" class="profile-btn">내 프로필</a>
                        <a href="/logout" class="logout-btn">로그아웃</a>
                    </div>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/auth/steam" class="steam-login-btn">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="steam-icon">
                            <path d="M11.979 0C5.678 0 .511 4.86.022 11.037l6.432 2.658c.545-.371 1.203-.59 1.912-.59.063 0 .125.004.188.006l2.861-4.142V8.91c0-2.495 2.028-4.524 4.524-4.524 2.494 0 4.524 2.029 4.524 4.524s-2.03 4.525-4.524 4.525h-.105l-4.076 2.911c0 .052.004.105.004.159 0 1.875-1.515 3.396-3.39 3.396-1.635 0-3.016-1.173-3.331-2.727L.436 15.27C1.5 20.16 6.345 24 11.979 24c6.624 0 11.99-5.367 11.99-11.99C23.969 5.367 18.603.001 11.979.001zM7.54 18.21l-1.473-.61c.262.543.714.999 1.314 1.25 1.297.539 2.793-.076 3.332-1.375.263-.63.264-1.319.005-1.949s-.75-1.121-1.377-1.383c-.624-.26-1.29-.249-1.878-.03l1.523.63c.956.4 1.409 1.5 1.009 2.454-.397.957-1.497 1.41-2.454 1.013H7.54zm9.423-11.94c0-1.662-1.353-3.015-3.015-3.015-1.665 0-3.015 1.353-3.015 3.015 0 1.665 1.35 3.015 3.015 3.015 1.662 0 3.015-1.35 3.015-3.015zm-5.271-.005c0-1.252 1.013-2.266 2.265-2.266 1.249 0 2.266 1.014 2.266 2.266 0 1.251-1.017 2.265-2.266 2.265-1.252 0-2.265-1.014-2.265-2.265z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Steam으로 로그인</span>
                    </a>
                <% } %>
                
                <a href="#" class="discord-btn">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="discord-icon">
                        <path d="M20.317 4.37a19.791 19.791 0 0 0-4.885-1.515a.074.074 0 0 0-.079.037c-.21.375-.444.864-.608 1.25a18.27 18.27 0 0 0-5.487 0a12.64 12.64 0 0 0-.617-1.25a.077.077 0 0 0-.079-.037A19.736 19.736 0 0 0 3.677 4.37a.07.07 0 0 0-.032.027C.533 9.046-.32 13.58.099 18.057a.082.082 0 0 0 .031.057a19.9 19.9 0 0 0 5.993 3.03a.078.078 0 0 0 .084-.028a14.09 14.09 0 0 0 1.226-1.994a.076.076 0 0 0-.041-.106a13.107 13.107 0 0 1-1.872-.892a.077.077 0 0 1-.008-.128a10.2 10.2 0 0 0 .372-.292a.074.074 0 0 1 .077-.01c3.928 1.793 8.18 1.793 12.062 0a.074.074 0 0 1 .078.01c.12.098.246.198.373.292a.077.077 0 0 1-.006.127a12.299 12.299 0 0 1-1.873.892a.077.077 0 0 0-.041.107c.36.698.772 1.362 1.225 1.993a.076.076 0 0 0 .084.028a19.839 19.839 0 0 0 6.002-3.03a.077.077 0 0 0 .032-.054c.5-5.177-.838-9.674-3.549-13.66a.061.061 0 0 0-.031-.03zM8.02 15.33c-1.183 0-2.157-1.085-2.157-2.419c0-1.333.956-2.419 2.157-2.419c1.21 0 2.176 1.096 2.157 2.42c0 1.333-.956 2.418-2.157 2.418zm7.975 0c-1.183 0-2.157-1.085-2.157-2.419c0-1.333.955-2.419 2.157-2.419c1.21 0 2.176 1.096 2.157 2.42c0 1.333-.946 2.418-2.157 2.418z"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Discord</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <%- body %>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <p>데드락은 밸브 코퍼레이션의 등록 상표입니다.</p>
            <p>© 2025 Rho Technologies LLC</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <span>개인정보 처리방침</span>
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">🌐</a>
                <a href="#">💬</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>